OL,3,C'Hairy moment' binmen avoid being hit
OL,4,Cby car
OL,6,FBlackburn with Darwen Council released
OL,7,Fthis footage on its Facebook page
OL,9,FThis is the 'hairy moment' two bin men
OL,10,Fwere nearly were nearly hit by a car
OL,11,Fafter an impatient driver mounted a
OL,12,Fpavement to get round their wagon.
OL,14,FBlackburn with Darwen Borough Council
OL,15,Fshared the footage on social media
OL,16,Ffollowing the "absolutely shocking"
OL,17,Fincident on Devon Road.
OL,19,FIt shows silver Volkswagen Polo
OL,20,Fmounting the pavement where the refuse
OL,21,Fteam were collecting the bins.
