OL,6,FCouncil bosses praised the "quick-
OL,7,Fthinking driver" of the wagon who
OL,8,Fsounded the horn to alert his
OL,9,Fcolleague, which avoided a collision.
OL,11,FThe driver, who has not been named,
OL,12,Fhas since received a warning letter
OL,13,Funder Section 43 of the Anti-Social
OL,14,FBehaviour Crime and Policing Act 2014.
OL,16,FIn a statement, Blackburn with Darwen
OL,17,FBorough Council said: "Our refuse team
OL,18,Fhad one hairy moment a couple of weeks
OL,19,Fago.
