OL,3,C'Hairy moment' binmen avoid being hit
OL,4,Cby car
OL,6,F"The driver in the silver car decided
OL,7,Fthey were too impatient to wait for
OL,8,Four collection vehicle, and mounted
OL,9,Fthe pavement where our team were
OL,10,Fcollecting the bins.
OL,12,F"Luckily, the quick-thinking driver of
OL,13,Fthe collection vehicle alerted his
OL,14,Fcolleagues by sounding the horn, which
OL,15,Favoided a collision.
OL,17,F"The driver of the silver car received
OL,18,Fa warning letter in accordance with
OL,19,FSection 43 of the Anti-Social
OL,20,FBehaviour Crime and Policing Act 2014.
