OL,6,F"If they partake in similar behaviour
OL,7,Fin future, they could be served with a
OL,8,Fcommunity protection notice with
OL,9,Ffurther action taken such as a fine or
OL,10,Fprosecution. In this case, our refuse
OL,11,Fcollection vehicle had no option but
OL,12,Fto take up the road because of parked
OL,13,Fvehicles.
OL,15,F"Please think before you park. And
OL,16,Fremember ` patience is a virtue."
