OL,6,FThe post has garnered lots of comments
OL,7,Fon the council's Facebook page, one
OL,8,Fperson said: "Should have got a ban or
OL,9,Flicense revoked. Absolutely shocking
OL,10,Fto mount a pavement, just because you
OL,11,Fcan't wait a few minutes and put
OL,12,Fpeople's lives at risk."
OL,14,FAnother wrote: "What an entitled
OL,15,Fdriver, there could have been a child
OL,16,Fstepping out from a house, as well as
OL,17,Fthe danger the driver put these
OL,18,Fworkers in."
